<div id="txtcont" class="span9" style="position: relative;">
    <p><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l7' data-llen='152:178'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0076', 'WYG', '010-1a' );" name="010-1a" class="pb">[010-1a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l8' data-llen='178:186'>欽定四庫全書</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l9' data-llen='186:195'>　大戴禮記卷十</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l10' data-llen='195:215'>　　　　　　　　　　　　漢　戴德　撰</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l11' data-llen='215:240'>　文王官人第七十一<span class='krp-note'>案各本改作七/十二今訂正</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l12' data-llen='240:272'>　諸侯遷廟第七十二<span class='krp-note'>案二或改作三或不改/故陳振孫云兩七十二</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l13' data-llen='272:303'>　諸侯釁廟第七十三<span class='krp-note'>案三或改作四或不改/故吳澄云兩七十三</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l14' data-llen='303:311'>　　文王官人</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l15' data-llen='311:329'>王曰太師慎維深思内觀民務察度情偽</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l16' data-llen='329:355'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0076', 'WYG', '010-1b' );" name="010-1b" class="pb">[010-1b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l17' data-llen='355:364'>　謂視中觀隱也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l18' data-llen='364:378'>變官民能厯其才藝女維敬哉</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l19' data-llen='378:390'>　試以衆位厯觀其才也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l20' data-llen='390:398'>女何慎乎非倫</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l21' data-llen='398:408'>　倫理次也宜所慎</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l22' data-llen='408:439'>倫有七屬屬有九用用有六徴<span class='krp-note'>案徴他本訛作/微今從劉本</span>一曰觀</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l23' data-llen='439:462'>誠二曰攷志三曰視中四曰觀色五曰觀隱六曰揆徳</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l24' data-llen='462:469'>　其說在下</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l25' data-llen='469:495'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0076', 'WYG', '010-2a' );" name="010-2a" class="pb">[010-2a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l26' data-llen='495:515'>王曰於乎女因方以觀之富貴者觀其禮施也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l27' data-llen='515:531'>　觀其禮及其施曲禮曰積而能散</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l28' data-llen='531:542'>貧窮者觀其有徳守也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l29' data-llen='542:558'>　觀其徳與其守孔子曰君子固窮</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l30' data-llen='558:578'>嬖寵者觀其不驕奢也隱約者觀其不懾懼也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l31' data-llen='578:601'>　曲禮曰富貴而知好禮則不驕不淫貧賤而知好禮</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l32' data-llen='601:608'>　則志不懾</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l33' data-llen='608:631'>其少觀其恭敬好學而能弟也其壯觀其絜亷務行而</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l34' data-llen='631:657'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0076', 'WYG', '010-2b' );" name="010-2b" class="pb">[010-2b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l35' data-llen='657:689'>勝其私也其老觀其憲慎<span class='krp-note'>案各本憲上衍/意字今從方本</span>强其所不足</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l36' data-llen='689:695'>而不踰也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l37' data-llen='695:718'>　孔子射矍相之圃蓋觀者如堵牆使公罔之裘序㸃</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l38' data-llen='718:741'>　揚觶而語公罔之裘揚觶而語曰幼壯孝弟耆耋好</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l39' data-llen='741:764'>　禮不從流俗修身以俟死者不在此位也蓋去者半</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l40' data-llen='764:787'>　處者半序㸃又揚觶而語曰好學不倦好禮不變旄</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l41' data-llen='787:806'>　期稱道不亂者不在此位也蓋㢙有存者</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l42' data-llen='806:829'>父子之間觀其孝慈也兄弟之間觀其和友也君臣之</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l43' data-llen='829:855'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0076', 'WYG', '010-3a' );" name="010-3a" class="pb">[010-3a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l44' data-llen='855:863'>間觀其忠惠也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l45' data-llen='863:879'>　父慈子孝兄友弟和君惠臣忠也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l46' data-llen='879:890'>鄉黨之間觀其信憚也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l47' data-llen='890:897'>　信而敬憚</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l48' data-llen='897:920'>省其居處觀其義方省其喪哀觀其貞良省其出入觀</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l49' data-llen='920:933'>其交友省其交友觀其任亷</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l50' data-llen='933:943'>　任以恩相親信也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l51' data-llen='943:975'>攷之以觀其信絜之以觀其知<span class='krp-note'>案絜字他本訛/作挈今從劉本</span>示之難</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l52' data-llen='975:1001'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0076', 'WYG', '010-3b' );" name="010-3b" class="pb">[010-3b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l53' data-llen='1001:1035'>以觀其勇煩之以觀其治<span class='krp-note'>案逸周書作煩之以事/以觀其治此脱二字</span>淹之</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l54' data-llen='1035:1053'>以利以觀其不貪藍之以樂以觀其不寧</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l55' data-llen='1053:1060'>　藍猶濫也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l56' data-llen='1060:1083'>喜之以物以觀其不輕怒之以觀其重醉之以觀其不</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l57' data-llen='1083:1106'>失也縱之以觀其常遠使之以觀其不貳邇之以觀其</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l58' data-llen='1106:1126'>不倦探取其志以觀其情攷其隂陽以觀其誠</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l59' data-llen='1126:1135'>　隂陽猶隱顯也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l60' data-llen='1135:1166'>覆其微言以觀其信曲省其行以觀其備<span class='krp-note'>案此下各本/衍成字今從</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l61' data-llen='1166:1192'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0076', 'WYG', '010-4a' );" name="010-4a" class="pb">[010-4a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l62' data-llen='1192:1219'><span class='krp-note'>方/本</span>此之謂觀誠也二曰方與之言以觀其志志殷而㴱</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l63' data-llen='1219:1229'>　殷盛也㴱蓋深也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l64' data-llen='1229:1252'>其氣寛以柔其色儉而不謟其禮先人其言後人見其</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l65' data-llen='1252:1262'>所不足曰日益者也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l66' data-llen='1262:1269'>　言日就益</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l67' data-llen='1269:1302'>好臨人以色<span class='krp-note'>案好各本訛作如今/從方本及逸周書</span>高人以氣賢人以言</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l68' data-llen='1302:1308'>防其不足</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l69' data-llen='1308:1315'>　不欲見之</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l70' data-llen='1315:1341'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0076', 'WYG', '010-4b' );" name="010-4b" class="pb">[010-4b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l71' data-llen='1341:1372'>伐其所能曰日損者也其貌直而不侮<span class='krp-note'>案侮他本訛作/傷今從劉本</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l72' data-llen='1372:1392'>其言正而不私不飾其美不隱其惡不防其過</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l73' data-llen='1392:1400'>　如日月之食</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l74' data-llen='1400:1431'>曰有質者也其貌固嫗其言工巧<span class='krp-note'>案嫗各本訛作嘔/注同今從方本</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l75' data-llen='1431:1446'>　嫗以耽色下人謂形柔而辭巧</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l76' data-llen='1446:1470'>飾其見物務其小徴<span class='krp-note'>案徴各本訛作/微今從方本</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l77' data-llen='1470:1488'>　有浮淺之事則工飾之而務尚其小成</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l78' data-llen='1488:1494'>以故自說</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l79' data-llen='1494:1520'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0076', 'WYG', '010-5a' );" name="010-5a" class="pb">[010-5a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l80' data-llen='1520:1529'>　言以事自解説</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l81' data-llen='1529:1551'>曰無質者也喜怒以物而色不作煩亂之而志不營</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l82' data-llen='1551:1558'>　營猶亂也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l83' data-llen='1558:1568'>深道以利而心不移</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l84' data-llen='1568:1576'>　道也者導也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l85' data-llen='1576:1599'>臨懾以威而氣不卑曰平心而固守者也喜怒以物而</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l86' data-llen='1599:1622'>變易知煩亂之而志不裕示之以利而易移臨懾以威</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l87' data-llen='1622:1653'>而易懾曰鄙心而假氣者也<span class='krp-note'>案假各本訛作/勢今從方本</span>執之以物</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l88' data-llen='1653:1679'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0076', 'WYG', '010-5b' );" name="010-5b" class="pb">[010-5b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l89' data-llen='1679:1708'>而遫決驚之以卒而度料<span class='krp-note'>案決字各本訛在/驚字下今從方本</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l90' data-llen='1708:1725'>　言引之以卒然之事而能應時度焉</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l91' data-llen='1725:1755'>不紊而性辨<span class='krp-note'>案紊各本訛作/學今從方本</span>曰有慮者也難投以物</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l92' data-llen='1755:1760'>　物事</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l93' data-llen='1760:1787'>難説以言知一而不可以解也<span class='krp-note'>案而各本作/如今從方本</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l94' data-llen='1787:1794'>　言因一端</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l95' data-llen='1794:1825'>困而不知其止無辨而自順<span class='krp-note'>案順各本作/慎今從方本</span>曰愚戇者也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l96' data-llen='1825:1841'><span class='krp-note'>案戇各本訛作/怒今從方本</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l97' data-llen='1841:1867'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0076', 'WYG', '010-6a' );" name="010-6a" class="pb">[010-6a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l98' data-llen='1867:1874'>　謂闇狼也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l99' data-llen='1874:1883'>營之以物而不虞</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l100' data-llen='1883:1898'>　虞度也至則攻辨之不豫計度</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l101' data-llen='1898:1929'>犯之以卒<span class='krp-note'>案之各本訛作/人今從方本</span>而不懼置義而不可遷臨之</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l102' data-llen='1929:1960'>以貨色<span class='krp-note'>案貨各本訛作/貸今從方本</span>而不可營曰絜亷而果敢者也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l103' data-llen='1960:1983'>　果敢謂不虞不懼也絜亷謂不營于貨色在義而不</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l104' data-llen='1983:1992'>　可遷則兼之也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l105' data-llen='1992:2021'>易移以言存志不能守固<span class='krp-note'>案固各本作/錮今從方本</span>已諾無斷</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l106' data-llen='2021:2047'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0076', 'WYG', '010-6b' );" name="010-6b" class="pb">[010-6b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l107' data-llen='2047:2062'>　言止慎諾于人又不能自裁斷</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l108' data-llen='2062:2085'>曰弱志者也順與之弗為喜非奪之弗為怒沈靜而寡</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l109' data-llen='2085:2093'>言多稽而儉貌</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l110' data-llen='2093:2099'>　稽攷也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l111' data-llen='2099:2133'>曰質靜者也辨言而不固行<span class='krp-note'>案此下各本衍有道而/先困五字今從方本</span>自</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l112' data-llen='2133:2173'>順而不讓<span class='krp-note'>案順各本作/慎今從方本</span>失當而强之<span class='krp-note'>案各本脱失字而/作如今從方本</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l113' data-llen='2173:2197'>曰妬誣者也<span class='krp-note'>案妬上各本衍始/字注同今從方本</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l114' data-llen='2197:2205'>　謂妬賢誣善</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l115' data-llen='2205:2231'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0076', 'WYG', '010-7a' );" name="010-7a" class="pb">[010-7a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l116' data-llen='2231:2254'>微情而能發<span class='krp-note'>案微情各本訛作/徴清今從方本</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l117' data-llen='2254:2263'>　謂攻發幽賾也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l118' data-llen='2263:2299'>度察而能盡曰志治者也<span class='krp-note'>案志治各本訛作/治志今從方本</span>華而誣<span class='krp-note'>案/而</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l119' data-llen='2299:2327'><span class='krp-note'>各本作如/今從方本</span>巧言令色足恭一也皆以無為有者也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l120' data-llen='2327:2339'>　子曰巧言令色鮮矣仁</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l121' data-llen='2339:2360'>此之謂攷志也<span class='krp-note'>案謂各本作/為今從方本</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l122' data-llen='2360:2367'>　攷度其志</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l123' data-llen='2367:2379'>三曰誠在其中此見于外</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l124' data-llen='2379:2405'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0076', 'WYG', '010-7b' );" name="010-7b" class="pb">[010-7b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l125' data-llen='2405:2413'>　此上之諸志</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l126' data-llen='2413:2421'>以其見占其隱</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l127' data-llen='2421:2430'>　按其陽察其隂</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l128' data-llen='2430:2438'>以其細占其大</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l129' data-llen='2438:2447'>　據其小省其大</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l130' data-llen='2447:2455'>以其聲處其氣</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l131' data-llen='2455:2464'>　聽處其聲氣也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l132' data-llen='2464:2486'>氣初生物<span class='krp-note'>案各本訛作初氣/生物今從方本</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l133' data-llen='2486:2512'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0076', 'WYG', '010-8a' );" name="010-8a" class="pb">[010-8a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l134' data-llen='2512:2521'>　謂物在于胞胎</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l135' data-llen='2521:2544'>物生有聲聲有剛有柔有濁有清有好有惡咸發于聲</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l136' data-llen='2544:2567'>也心氣華誕者其聲流散心氣順信者其聲順節心氣</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l137' data-llen='2567:2599'>鄙戾者其聲斯醜<span class='krp-note'>案斯各本作嘶/乃因注文而改</span>心氣寛柔者其聲温</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l138' data-llen='2599:2602'>好</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l139' data-llen='2602:2625'>　嘶當聲誤為斯春秋左傳曰蜂目豺聲忍人也夫音</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l140' data-llen='2625:2641'>　之美惡尚通于金石而況于身乎</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l141' data-llen='2641:2651'>信氣中易義氣時舒</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l142' data-llen='2651:2677'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0076', 'WYG', '010-8b' );" name="010-8b" class="pb">[010-8b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l143' data-llen='2677:2691'>　義者剛其氣亦充故舒縱也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l144' data-llen='2691:2697'>智氣簡備</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l145' data-llen='2697:2702'>　簡通</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l146' data-llen='2702:2731'>勇氣壯直聽其聲處其氣攷其所為觀其所由<span class='krp-note'>案此下/各本有</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l147' data-llen='2731:2760'><span class='krp-note'>察其所安四字乃後人/因論語加入今從方本</span>以其前占其後</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l148' data-llen='2760:2769'>　以前行占後行</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l149' data-llen='2769:2792'>以其見占其隱以其小占其大此之謂視中也四曰民</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l150' data-llen='2792:2803'>有五性喜怒欲懼憂也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l151' data-llen='2803:2829'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0076', 'WYG', '010-9a' );" name="010-9a" class="pb">[010-9a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l152' data-llen='2829:2852'>　喜怒欲懼憂以其俱生于人而有常故亦謂之性也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l153' data-llen='2852:2864'>　此五者之性人心兼盡</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l154' data-llen='2864:2887'>喜氣内畜雖欲隱之陽喜必見怒氣内畜雖欲隱之陽</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l155' data-llen='2887:2910'>怒必見欲氣内畜雖欲隱之陽欲必見懼氣内畜雖欲</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l156' data-llen='2910:2933'>隱之陽懼必見憂悲之氣内畜雖欲隱之陽憂必見五</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l157' data-llen='2933:2954'>氣誠于中發形于外民情不隱也喜色由然以生</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l158' data-llen='2954:2967'>　由當為油油然新生好貌</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l159' data-llen='2967:2995'>怒色拂然以侮欲色嫗然以偷<span class='krp-note'>案嫗各本訛作/嘔今從方本</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l160' data-llen='2995:3021'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0076', 'WYG', '010-9b' );" name="010-9b" class="pb">[010-9b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l161' data-llen='3021:3033'>　偷茍且也言惟求悦人</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l162' data-llen='3033:3049'>懼色薄然以下憂悲之色纍然而靜</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l163' data-llen='3049:3060'>　玉藻曰喪容纍纍也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l164' data-llen='3060:3083'>誠智必有難盡之色誠仁必有可尊之色誠勇必有難</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l165' data-llen='3083:3106'>懾之色誠忠必有可親之色誠絜必有難汚之色誠靜</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l166' data-llen='3106:3129'>必有可信之色質色皓然固以安偽色縵然亂以煩雖</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l167' data-llen='3129:3139'>欲故之中色不聽也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l168' data-llen='3139:3162'>　言雖欲故隱之于中而無奈色見于外故子夏問孝</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l169' data-llen='3162:3189'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0076', 'WYG', '010-10a' );" name="010-10a" class="pb">[010-10a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l170' data-llen='3189:3207'>　子曰色難是以君子戒慎不失色于人</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l171' data-llen='3207:3235'>雖變可知此之謂觀色也五曰生民有霒陽<span class='krp-note'>案霒即/古隂字</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l172' data-llen='3235:3256'>　言人含隂陽之氣生而有知有知故生機偽也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l173' data-llen='3256:3288'>人多隱其情飾其偽<span class='krp-note'>案人下各本衍/有字今從方本</span>以賴于物以攻其</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l174' data-llen='3288:3311'>名也有隱于仁質者有隱于知理者有隱于文藝者有</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l175' data-llen='3311:3334'>隱于亷勇者有隱于忠孝者有隱于交友者如此者不</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l176' data-llen='3334:3365'>可不察也小施而好大得小讓而好大爭<span class='krp-note'>案各本訛作/大事今從方</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l177' data-llen='3365:3376'><span class='krp-note'>本/</span>言願以為質</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l178' data-llen='3376:3403'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0076', 'WYG', '010-10b' );" name="010-10b" class="pb">[010-10b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l179' data-llen='3403:3413'>　愿當聲誤為願也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l180' data-llen='3413:3430'>偽愛以為忠面寛而貌慈假節以示之</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l181' data-llen='3430:3440'>　假節假仁質之節</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l182' data-llen='3440:3457'>故其行以攻其名如此者隱于仁質也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l183' data-llen='3457:3468'>　故其行者故為是行</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l184' data-llen='3468:3492'>推前恃忠府知物焉<span class='krp-note'>案恃各本訛作/惡今從方本</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l185' data-llen='3492:3515'>　謂有詢議之攻其所不知者則推援于人而恃以為</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l186' data-llen='3515:3528'>　忠府而形貌又如曉然也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l187' data-llen='3528:3555'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0076', 'WYG', '010-11a' );" name="010-11a" class="pb">[010-11a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l188' data-llen='3555:3565'>首成功少其所不足</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l189' data-llen='3565:3587'>　謂有先功者因首之有不足者因薄之詐以為知</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l190' data-llen='3587:3610'>慮誠不及佯為不言内誠不足色示有餘故知以動人</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l191' data-llen='3610:3631'>自執而不讓<span class='krp-note'>案執各本訛作/順今從方本</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l192' data-llen='3631:3654'>　及其不知也觀人之動止因執為意而不推讓于人</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l193' data-llen='3654:3658'>　也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l194' data-llen='3658:3669'>錯辭而不遂莫知其情</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l195' data-llen='3669:3691'>　本非其意故辭情不終詩云虵虵碩言出自口矣</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l196' data-llen='3691:3718'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0076', 'WYG', '010-11b' );" name="010-11b" class="pb">[010-11b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l197' data-llen='3718:3734'>如是者隱于知理者也素動人以言</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l198' data-llen='3734:3752'>　謂先徧習之及于衆前為方欲陳說也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l199' data-llen='3752:3759'>涉物而不終</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l200' data-llen='3759:3771'>　務廣聞而不究其言也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l201' data-llen='3771:3800'>問則不對詳為不窮<span class='krp-note'>案詳佯/古通用</span>色示有餘有道而自順用</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l202' data-llen='3800:3829'>之物<span class='krp-note'>案逸周書有作假用作/因之下缺一字物作初</span>窮則為深</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l203' data-llen='3829:3836'>　妄言深遠</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l204' data-llen='3836:3852'>如此者隱于文藝者也亷言以為氣</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l205' data-llen='3852:3879'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0076', 'WYG', '010-12a' );" name="010-12a" class="pb">[010-12a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l206' data-llen='3879:3892'>　茍作亷言以見俠氣自然</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l207' data-llen='3892:3932'>矯厲以為勇<span class='krp-note'>案矯各本訛作/驕今從逸周書</span>内恐外悻<span class='krp-note'>案各本訛作/悴今從劉本</span>無</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l208' data-llen='3932:3955'>所不至敬再其説<span class='krp-note'>案敬再當從逸/周書作亟稱</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l209' data-llen='3955:3977'>　言茍自矯厲持以為勇終必恐懾而更至恭佞也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l210' data-llen='3977:4000'>以詐臨人如此者隱于亷勇者也自事其親好以告人</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l211' data-llen='4000:4006'>乞言勞醉</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l212' data-llen='4006:4013'>　醉言悴也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l213' data-llen='4013:4036'>而面于敬愛飾其見物故得其名名揚于外不誠于内</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l214' data-llen='4036:4063'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0076', 'WYG', '010-12b' );" name="010-12b" class="pb">[010-12b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l215' data-llen='4063:4076'>伐名以事其親戚以故取利</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l216' data-llen='4076:4087'>　以如此故要取其利</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l217' data-llen='4087:4110'>分自其名以私其身如此者隱于忠孝者也隂行以取</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l218' data-llen='4110:4113'>名</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l219' data-llen='4113:4124'>　隂行謂竊求諸人也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l220' data-llen='4124:4131'>比周以相譽</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l221' data-llen='4131:4142'>　迭相親比交相談譽</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l222' data-llen='4142:4161'>明知賢可以徴與左右不同而交交必重己</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l223' data-llen='4161:4188'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0076', 'WYG', '010-13a' );" name="010-13a" class="pb">[010-13a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l224' data-llen='4188:4207'>　言知其賢而不與交交必取其重己者也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l225' data-llen='4207:4230'>心説之而身不近之身近之而實不至而懽忠不盡懽</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l226' data-llen='4230:4240'>忠盡見于衆而貌克</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l227' data-llen='4240:4257'>　雖盡其忠懽及衆人之前猶相克爭</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l228' data-llen='4257:4280'>如此者隱于交友者也此之謂觀隱也六曰言行不類</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l229' data-llen='4280:4303'>終始相悖隂陽克易外内不合雖有隱節見行曰非誠</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l230' data-llen='4303:4308'>質者也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l231' data-llen='4308:4319'>　隱節隱于仁質之等</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l232' data-llen='4319:4346'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0076', 'WYG', '010-13b' );" name="010-13b" class="pb">[010-13b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l233' data-llen='4346:4368'>其言甚忠其行甚平其志無私施不在多靜而寡類</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l234' data-llen='4368:4374'>　不好狎</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l235' data-llen='4374:4413'>莊而安人<span class='krp-note'>案莊各本訛作/財今從方本</span>曰有仁心者也<span class='krp-note'>案仁各本訛/作行今從方</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l236' data-llen='4413:4434'><span class='krp-note'>本/</span>事變而能治物善而能説浚窮而能達</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l237' data-llen='4434:4440'>　浚深也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l238' data-llen='4440:4471'>錯身立方而能遂曰廣知者也少言而行<span class='krp-note'>案而各本作/如今從方本</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l239' data-llen='4471:4487'>恭儉以讓有知而不伐有施而不置</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l240' data-llen='4487:4496'>　心不形于色也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l241' data-llen='4496:4523'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0076', 'WYG', '010-14a' );" name="010-14a" class="pb">[010-14a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l242' data-llen='4523:4539'>曰慎謙良者也微忽之言乆而可復</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l243' data-llen='4539:4550'>　謂微細及忽然之語</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l244' data-llen='4550:4560'>幽閒之行獨而不克</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l245' data-llen='4560:4568'>　克好勝人也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l246' data-llen='4568:4576'>行其亡如其存</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l247' data-llen='4576:4589'>　謂奉先君及祖考之教令</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l248' data-llen='4589:4612'>曰順信者也貴富雖尊恭儉而能施衆强嚴威有禮而</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l249' data-llen='4612:4635'>不驕曰有徳者也隱約而不懾安樂而不奢勤勞之不</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l250' data-llen='4635:4662'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0076', 'WYG', '010-14b' );" name="010-14b" class="pb">[010-14b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l251' data-llen='4662:4700'>變喜怒之而度晰<span class='krp-note'>案而各本作/如今從方本</span>曰有守者也<span class='krp-note'>案各本曰/訛作日脱</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l252' data-llen='4700:4713'><span class='krp-note'>有字者字/今從方本</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l253' data-llen='4713:4731'>　晰明也有喜怒之來能置量度而明焉</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l254' data-llen='4731:4752'>直方而不毁<span class='krp-note'>案直各本訛作/置今從方本</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l255' data-llen='4752:4759'>　不瓦合也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l256' data-llen='4759:4791'>亷絜而不戾强立而無私<span class='krp-note'>案强立各本訛作/立强今從方本</span>曰有經者</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l257' data-llen='4791:4812'>也<span class='krp-note'>案各本脱有/字今從方本</span>正靜以待命</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l258' data-llen='4812:4818'>　命期命</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l259' data-llen='4818:4845'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0076', 'WYG', '010-15a' );" name="010-15a" class="pb">[010-15a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l260' data-llen='4845:4868'>不召不至不問不言言不過行行不過道曰沈靜者也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l261' data-llen='4868:4899'>忠愛以事其親歡欣以致之<span class='krp-note'>案致各本訛作/敬今從方本</span>盡力而不</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l262' data-llen='4899:4931'>面敬以安人以故名不生焉<span class='krp-note'>案故字各本在名/字下今從方本</span>曰忠孝</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l263' data-llen='4931:4962'>者也合志而同方<span class='krp-note'>案而各本作/如今從方本</span>共其憂而任其難行忠</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l264' data-llen='4962:4985'>信而不相疑迷隱遠而不相舍曰至友者也心色辭氣</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l265' data-llen='4985:4992'>其入人甚俞</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l266' data-llen='4992:5000'>　甚俞言無己</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l267' data-llen='5000:5005'>進退工</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l268' data-llen='5005:5032'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0076', 'WYG', '010-15b' );" name="010-15b" class="pb">[010-15b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l269' data-llen='5032:5038'>　工能也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l270' data-llen='5038:5061'>故其與人甚巧其就人甚速其叛人甚易曰位志者也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l271' data-llen='5061:5084'>　位志者言其不一如爵位及人志也位有高卑人各</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l272' data-llen='5084:5090'>　有志也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l273' data-llen='5090:5113'>飲食以親貨賄以交接利以合故得望譽征利而依隱</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l274' data-llen='5113:5122'>于物曰貪鄙者也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l275' data-llen='5122:5137'>　妄當聲誤為望征行也隱據也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l276' data-llen='5137:5145'>質不斷辭不至</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l277' data-llen='5145:5172'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0076', 'WYG', '010-16a' );" name="010-16a" class="pb">[010-16a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l278' data-llen='5172:5187'>　言心既不能裁斷而辭又不及</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l279' data-llen='5187:5210'>少其所不足謀而不已曰偽詐者也言行亟變從容謬</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l280' data-llen='5210:5213'>易</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l281' data-llen='5213:5220'>　安然反覆</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l282' data-llen='5220:5243'>好惡無常行身不類曰無誠志者也小知而不大決小</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l283' data-llen='5243:5266'>能而不大成顧小物而不知大論亟變而多私曰華誕</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l284' data-llen='5266:5275'>者也規諫而不類</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l285' data-llen='5275:5286'>　言能規諫而反不類</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l286' data-llen='5286:5313'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0076', 'WYG', '010-16b' );" name="010-16b" class="pb">[010-16b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l287' data-llen='5313:5320'>道行而不平</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l288' data-llen='5320:5331'>　言以道行復不平也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l289' data-llen='5331:5349'>曰巧名者也故事阻者不夷畸鬼者不仁</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l290' data-llen='5349:5360'>　恃禱祀而不自修也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l291' data-llen='5360:5377'>面譽者不忠飾貌者不情隱節者不平</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l292' data-llen='5377:5389'>　隱節者亦謂六隱之等</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l293' data-llen='5389:5406'>多私者不義揚言者寡信此之謂揆徳</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l294' data-llen='5406:5415'>　謂揆度于徳也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l295' data-llen='5415:5442'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0076', 'WYG', '010-17a' );" name="010-17a" class="pb">[010-17a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l296' data-llen='5442:5465'>王曰太師女推其往言以揆其來行聽其來言以省其</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l297' data-llen='5465:5469'>往行</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l298' data-llen='5469:5492'>　孔子曰始吾於人聽其言而信其行今吾於人聽其</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l299' data-llen='5492:5501'>　言而觀其行也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l300' data-llen='5501:5524'>觀其陽以攷其隂察其内以揆其外是故隱節者可知</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l301' data-llen='5524:5547'>偽飾無情者可辨質誠居善者可得忠惠守義者可見</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l302' data-llen='5547:5567'>也王曰於乎敬哉女何慎乎非心何慎乎非人</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l303' data-llen='5567:5580'>　言當内慎其心外慎于人</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l304' data-llen='5580:5607'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0076', 'WYG', '010-17b' );" name="010-17b" class="pb">[010-17b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l305' data-llen='5607:5630'>人有六徴六徴既成以觀九用九用既立一曰取平仁</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l306' data-llen='5630:5653'>而有慮者二曰取慈惠而有理者三曰取直愍而忠正</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l307' data-llen='5653:5688'>者<span class='krp-note'>案愍下舊注一作質乃/校書者語非盧氏注文</span>四曰取順直而察聽者五曰</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l308' data-llen='5688:5711'>取臨事而絜正者六曰取慎察而絜亷者七曰取好謀</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l309' data-llen='5711:5742'>而知務者<span class='krp-note'>案好下舊注一作/巧亦校書者語</span>八曰取接給而廣中者</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l310' data-llen='5742:5761'>　接給謂應所問而勤廣中謂博于聞識也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l311' data-llen='5761:5784'>九曰取猛毅而度斷者此之謂九用也平仁而有慮者</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l312' data-llen='5784:5795'>使是治國家而長百姓</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l313' data-llen='5795:5822'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0076', 'WYG', '010-18a' );" name="010-18a" class="pb">[010-18a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l314' data-llen='5822:5831'>　國諸侯家采邑</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l315' data-llen='5831:5848'>慈惠而有理者使是長鄉邑而治父子</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l316' data-llen='5848:5857'>　鄉鄉遂邑公邑</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l317' data-llen='5857:5874'>直愍而忠正者使是莅百官而察善否</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l318' data-llen='5874:5883'>　于周禮則治官</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l319' data-llen='5883:5902'>慎直而察聽者使是長民之獄訟出納辭令</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l320' data-llen='5902:5911'>　于周禮則刑官</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l321' data-llen='5911:5928'>臨事而絜正者使是守内藏而治出入</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l322' data-llen='5928:5955'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0076', 'WYG', '010-18b' );" name="010-18b" class="pb">[010-18b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l323' data-llen='5955:5964'>　于周禮則天官</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l324' data-llen='5964:5981'>慎察而絜㢘者使是分財臨貨主賞賜</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l325' data-llen='5981:5992'>　于周禮則司祿司勲</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l326' data-llen='5992:6022'>好謀而知務者使是治壤地而長百工<span class='krp-note'>案各本脱是/字今從方本</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l327' data-llen='6022:6035'>　于周禮則遂人匠車之等</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l328' data-llen='6035:6052'>接給而廣中者使是治諸侯而待賓客</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l329' data-llen='6052:6063'>　于周禮則行人掌客</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l330' data-llen='6063:6079'>猛毅而度斷者使是治軍事衞邊境</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l331' data-llen='6079:6106'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0076', 'WYG', '010-19a' );" name="010-19a" class="pb">[010-19a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l332' data-llen='6106:6116'>　于周禮則政官也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l333' data-llen='6116:6139'>因方而用之此之謂官能也九用有徴乃任七屬一曰</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l334' data-llen='6139:6145'>國則任貴</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l335' data-llen='6145:6156'>　周禮曰長以貴得民</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l336' data-llen='6156:6164'>二曰鄉則任貞</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l337' data-llen='6164:6180'>　幹事曰貞周禮曰吏以治得民也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l338' data-llen='6180:6188'>三曰官則任長</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l339' data-llen='6188:6204'>　周禮曰大事聽其長小事則專達</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l340' data-llen='6204:6231'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0076', 'WYG', '010-19b' );" name="010-19b" class="pb">[010-19b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l341' data-llen='6231:6239'>四曰學則任師</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l342' data-llen='6239:6250'>　周禮曰師以賢得民</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l343' data-llen='6250:6258'>五曰族則任宗</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l344' data-llen='6258:6269'>　周禮曰宗以族得民</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l345' data-llen='6269:6277'>六曰家則任主</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l346' data-llen='6277:6293'>　易曰家人有嚴君焉父母之謂也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l347' data-llen='6293:6316'>七曰先則任賢正月王親命七屬之人曰於乎慎維深</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l348' data-llen='6316:6336'>思内觀民務本慎在人女平心去私慎用六證</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l349' data-llen='6336:6363'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0076', 'WYG', '010-20a' );" name="010-20a" class="pb">[010-20a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l350' data-llen='6363:6371'>　六證六徴也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l351' data-llen='6371:6381'>論辨九用以交一人</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l352' data-llen='6381:6391'>　一人文王自謂也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l353' data-llen='6391:6414'>予亦不私女廢朕命亂我法罪致不赦三戒然後及論</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l354' data-llen='6414:6430'>　三戒之後亂法者則有司課其罪</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l355' data-llen='6430:6442'>王親受而攷之然後論成</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l356' data-llen='6442:6450'>　　諸侯遷廟</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l357' data-llen='6450:6473'>成廟將遷之新廟君前徙三日齋祝宗人及從者皆齋</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l358' data-llen='6473:6500'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0076', 'WYG', '010-20b' );" name="010-20b" class="pb">[010-20b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l359' data-llen='6500:6523'>　謂親過高祖則毁廟以昭穆遷之春秋榖梁傳曰作</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l360' data-llen='6523:6546'>　主壞廟有時日于練焉壞廟壞廟之道易簷可也改</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l361' data-llen='6546:6570'>　塗可也范甯云將納新神故示有所加焉鄭𤣥注士</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l362' data-llen='6570:6593'>　虞禮曰練而後遷也禮志云遷廟者更釁其廟而移</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l363' data-llen='6593:6612'>　故主焉按此篇成廟之文與榖梁相傅也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l364' data-llen='6612:6627'>徙之日君𤣥服從者皆𤣥服</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l365' data-llen='6627:6650'>　周禮司服職曰公之服自衮冕而下如王之服侯伯</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l366' data-llen='6650:6673'>　之服自鷩冕而下如公之服子男之服自毳冕而下</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l367' data-llen='6673:6700'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0076', 'WYG', '010-21a' );" name="010-21a" class="pb">[010-21a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l368' data-llen='6700:6723'>　如侯伯之服孤之服自絺冕而下如子男之服卿大</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l369' data-llen='6723:6747'>　夫之服自𤣥冕而下如孤之服玉藻曰君命屈狄再</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l370' data-llen='6747:6770'>　命褘衣内司服職曰辨外内命婦之服鞠衣展衣緣</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l371' data-llen='6770:6793'>　衣素紗其于祭也君與夫人皆申其服祭統曰公衮</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l372' data-llen='6793:6816'>　冕立于阼夫人副褘立于東房是也臣及命婦助祭</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l373' data-llen='6816:6839'>　于君皆盡其服自祭于家咸降一等隂爵不敢申也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l374' data-llen='6839:6862'>　雜記曰大夫冕而祭于公弁而祭于己士弁而祭于</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l375' data-llen='6862:6885'>　公冠而祭于己特牲饋食禮曰主婦纚笄宵衣立于</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l376' data-llen='6885:6912'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0076', 'WYG', '010-21b' );" name="010-21b" class="pb">[010-21b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l377' data-llen='6912:6936'>　房中是也然鄭氏頓貶公侯使一同𤣥冕以祭于己</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l378' data-llen='6936:6959'>　非其差也且諸侯專國禮樂車服王命有之何獨抑</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l379' data-llen='6959:6983'>　其服乎玉藻曰𤣥端以祭裨冕以朝孫炎云端當為</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l380' data-llen='6983:7007'>　冕𤣥冕祭服之下也其祭先君亦裨冕矣孫説為合</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l381' data-llen='7007:7030'>　下未即吉故略同爵弁也君命屈狄與再命褘衣者</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l382' data-llen='7030:7053'>　謂其夫為君則命其妻以屈狄加再等之命則上公</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l383' data-llen='7053:7076'>　夫人乃褘衣孫鄭等改鞠衣非也又云一命展衣者</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l384' data-llen='7076:7099'>　此則申子男臣妻之服耳言小國臣妻一命者亦展</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l385' data-llen='7099:7126'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0076', 'WYG', '010-22a' );" name="010-22a" class="pb">[010-22a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l386' data-llen='7126:7150'>　衣不命者則亦緣衣鄭𤣥又分公卿大夫及其妻為</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l387' data-llen='7150:7174'>　三等而升降其服經云孤絺冕卿大夫𤣥冕何為易</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l388' data-llen='7174:7197'>　之又命小國之卿及内子更同列國之卿孤絺冕與</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l389' data-llen='7197:7210'>　鞠衣錯易其次尤非宜也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l390' data-llen='7210:7216'>從至于廟</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l391' data-llen='7216:7222'>　廟殯宫</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l392' data-llen='7222:7229'>羣臣如朝位</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l393' data-llen='7229:7242'>　列于廟門外如路門之位</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l394' data-llen='7242:7269'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0076', 'WYG', '010-22b' );" name="010-22b" class="pb">[010-22b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l395' data-llen='7269:7285'>君入立于阼階下西向有司如朝位</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l396' data-llen='7285:7297'>　立于門内如門外之位</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l397' data-llen='7297:7320'>宗人擯舉手曰有司具請升君升祝奉幣從在左北面</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l398' data-llen='7320:7341'>　祝主辭故在左神將遷故出在户牖間南面矣</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l399' data-llen='7341:7364'>再拜興祝聲三曰孝嗣侯某敢以嘉幣告于皇考某侯</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l400' data-llen='7364:7380'>　言嗣以遷代不言國未忍有之也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l401' data-llen='7380:7388'>成廟將徙敢告</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l402' data-llen='7388:7407'>　卒不奠幣者禮畢矣于此將有事于新廟</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l403' data-llen='7407:7434'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0076', 'WYG', '010-23a' );" name="010-23a" class="pb">[010-23a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l404' data-llen='7434:7457'>君及祝再拜興祝曰請導君降立于階下奉衣服者皆</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l405' data-llen='7457:7463'>奉以從祝</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l406' data-llen='7463:7486'>　不言奉主而稱奉衣服者以毁易祖考誠人神之不</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l407' data-llen='7486:7509'>　忍從祝者祝所以導神也言皆者衣服非一稱周禮</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l408' data-llen='7509:7530'>　守祧職曰掌先王先公之廟祧其遺衣服藏焉</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l409' data-llen='7530:7553'>奉衣服者降堂君及在位者皆辟也奉衣服者至碑君</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l410' data-llen='7553:7576'>從有司皆以次從出廟門奉衣服者升車乃步君升車</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l411' data-llen='7576:7584'>從者皆就車也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l412' data-llen='7584:7611'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0076', 'WYG', '010-23b' );" name="010-23b" class="pb">[010-23b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l413' data-llen='7611:7622'>　皆就車謂乗貳車者</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l414' data-llen='7622:7635'>凡出入門及大溝渠祝下擯</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l415' data-llen='7635:7649'>　神車祝為左故于步處則下</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l416' data-llen='7649:7660'>至于新廟筵于户牖間</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l417' data-llen='7660:7671'>　始自外來故先于堂</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l418' data-llen='7671:7678'>樽于西序下</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l419' data-llen='7678:7701'>　四時之祭在室筵奥中在堂筵序下是以設樽恒于</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l420' data-llen='7701:7723'>　東方今惟布南面之席故置樽于西以因其便矣</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l421' data-llen='7723:7750'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0076', 'WYG', '010-24a' );" name="010-24a" class="pb">[010-24a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l422' data-llen='7750:7758'>脯醢陳于房中</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l423' data-llen='7758:7771'>　房西房也諸侯左右房也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l424' data-llen='7771:7783'>設洗當東榮南北以堂深</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l425' data-llen='7783:7794'>　記因卿士當言東霤</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l426' data-llen='7794:7817'>有司皆先入如朝位祝導奉衣服者乃入君從奉衣服</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l427' data-llen='7817:7823'>者入門左</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l428' data-llen='7823:7830'>　門左門西</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l429' data-llen='7830:7853'>在位者皆辟也奉衣服者升堂皆反位君從升奠衣服</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l430' data-llen='7853:7880'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0076', 'WYG', '010-24b' );" name="010-24b" class="pb">[010-24b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l431' data-llen='7880:7903'>于席上祝奠幣于几東君北向祝在左贊者盥升適房</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l432' data-llen='7903:7926'>薦脯醢君盥酌奠于薦西反位君及祝再拜興祝聲三</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l433' data-llen='7926:7949'>曰孝嗣侯某敢用嘉幣告于皇考某侯今月吉日可以</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l434' data-llen='7949:7971'>徙于新廟敢告再拜君就東廂西面祝就西廂東面</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l435' data-llen='7971:7986'>　東西侯也祝就西廂因其便也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l436' data-llen='7986:7998'>在位者皆反走辟如食間</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l437' data-llen='7998:8005'>　走疾趨也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l438' data-llen='8005:8028'>擯者舉手曰請反位君反位祝從在左卿大夫及衆有</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l439' data-llen='8028:8055'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0076', 'WYG', '010-25a' );" name="010-25a" class="pb">[010-25a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l440' data-llen='8055:8078'>司諸在位者皆反位祝聲三曰孝嗣侯某絜為而明薦</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l441' data-llen='8078:8082'>之享</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l442' data-llen='8082:8095'>　詩曰吉蠲為饎是用孝享</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l443' data-llen='8095:8105'>君及祝再拜君反位</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l444' data-llen='8105:8112'>　東郟之位</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l445' data-llen='8112:8118'>祝徹反位</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l446' data-llen='8118:8125'>　西郟之位</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l447' data-llen='8125:8148'>擯者曰遷廟事畢請就燕君出廟門卿大夫有司執事</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l448' data-llen='8148:8175'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0076', 'WYG', '010-25b' );" name="010-25b" class="pb">[010-25b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l449' data-llen='8175:8185'>者皆出廟門告事畢</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l450' data-llen='8185:8202'>　事謂内主藏衣服斂幣徹几筵之等</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l451' data-llen='8202:8211'>乃曰擇日而祭焉</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l452' data-llen='8211:8218'>　所以安神</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l453' data-llen='8218:8226'>　　諸侯釁廟</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l454' data-llen='8226:8234'>成廟釁之以羊</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l455' data-llen='8234:8257'>　廟新成而釁者尊而神之祭器名者成則釁之以豭</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l456' data-llen='8257:8261'>　豚</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l457' data-llen='8261:8288'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0076', 'WYG', '010-26a' );" name="010-26a" class="pb">[010-26a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l458' data-llen='8288:8312'>君𤣥服立于寢門内南向祝宗人宰夫雍人皆𤣥服</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l459' data-llen='8312:8333'>　以神事故亦同爵弁小戴君朝服者謂不與也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l460' data-llen='8333:8353'>宗人曰請命以釁某廟君曰諾遂入雍人拭羊</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l461' data-llen='8353:8358'>　拭捝</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l462' data-llen='8358:8371'>乃行入廟門碑南北面東上</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l463' data-llen='8371:8385'>　東上者宰夫也宰夫攝主也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l464' data-llen='8385:8408'>雍人舉羊升屋自中中屋南面刲羊血流于前乃降門</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l465' data-llen='8408:8418'>以雞有司當門北面</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l466' data-llen='8418:8445'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0076', 'WYG', '010-26b' );" name="010-26b" class="pb">[010-26b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l467' data-llen='8445:8456'>　有司宰夫祝宗人也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l468' data-llen='8456:8479'>雍人割雞屋下當門郟室割雞于室中有司亦北面也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l469' data-llen='8479:8502'>　郟室門郟之室一曰東西廂也釁東西室有司猶北</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l470' data-llen='8502:8525'>　面統于廟也雜記曰雍人舉羊升屋自中中屋南向</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l471' data-llen='8525:8548'>　刲羊血流于前乃降門郟室皆用雞先門而後郟室</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l472' data-llen='8548:8571'>　其衈皆于屋下割雞門當門郟室中室有司皆鄉室</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l473' data-llen='8571:8594'>　而立門則有司當門北面按小戴割雞亦于屋上記</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l474' data-llen='8594:8607'>　者不同耳此不言衈略也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l475' data-llen='8607:8634'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0076', 'WYG', '010-27a' );" name="010-27a" class="pb">[010-27a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l476' data-llen='8634:8657'>既事宗人告事畢皆退反命于君君寢門中南向宗人</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l477' data-llen='8657:8678'>曰釁某廟事畢君曰諾宗人請就燕君揖之乃退</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l478' data-llen='8678:8681'>　</span><br/>
